[Guest 2]: Decision-making you would be the more important part of the family and therefore family will eventually respect you

00:06:08.560 --> 00:06:12.160
[Guest 2]: So that was my theory, but when I entered into this project

00:06:12.160 --> 00:06:17.680
[Guest 2]: I realized that other than the fact that 20 million jobs is a huge task as Yazeed would have told you

00:06:18.400 --> 00:06:23.800
[Guest 2]: The problem with female labor employment ratio is completely different from the rest of the problem

00:06:24.640 --> 00:06:28.680
[Guest 2]: Unlike the rest of the problem where there's a linear growth, but not at the pace at which we want

00:06:29.440 --> 00:06:35.880
