00:06:35.880 --> 00:06:42.480
[Guest 2]: Leave apart the fact that we don't have enough women working. We also do not have enough women

00:06:43.000 --> 00:06:48.440
[Amit Varma]: The women who were working are leaving the workforce and this is something that blows my mind because I automatically assumed that hey

00:06:48.440 --> 00:06:49.160
[Amit Varma]: Things are really bad

00:06:49.160 --> 00:06:53.320
[Amit Varma]: but this is really getting better and therefore you'd imagine that more women are entering the workforce and

00:06:53.360 --> 00:06:58.760
