00:09:37.320 --> 00:09:41.920
[Amit Varma]: Cost if they weren't, you know washing dishes and doing whatever and if right from the start

00:09:41.920 --> 00:09:44.760
[Amit Varma]: They'd got an education and they were out working. They'd be earning so much more

00:09:44.760 --> 00:09:50.280
[Amit Varma]: So their time is not worth what your mate plus cook plus sweeper is, you know, those services are worth

00:09:50.280 --> 00:09:52.280
